  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "5-7. Ashtoreth—Astarte,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Milcom—Molech,",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and Chemosh—He built altars for these three; but, although he is described (1Ki 11:8) as doing the same for \"all his strange wives,\" there is no evidence that they had idols distinct from these; and there is no trace whatever of Egyptian idolatry.",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
